@PaymentService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5204
@access_token = replace-with-token

### Create payment intent
POST {{PaymentService_HostAddress}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"orderId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
	"amount": 49.99,
	"currency": "usd",
	"paymentMethodId": "pm_card_visa",
	"description": "Sample order"
}

### Fetch payments (finance scope)
GET {{PaymentService_HostAddress}}/api/payments?status=Succeeded
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Refund payment
POST {{PaymentService_HostAddress}}/api/payments/{{paymentId}}/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"amount": 10.00,
	"reason": "partial-refund"
}
